citations:
    citation-agot-daenerys-i:
        source: source-agot
        properties:
            locator: "Daenerys I"
            accessed: "2026-03-06"
        notes: "POV: Daenerys. Dany and Viserys are guests of Magister Illyrio Mopatis in Pentos. Viserys intends to marry Dany to Khal Drogo in exchange for a Dothraki army. Dany meets Drogo at Illyrio's feast, also meeting Ser Jorah Mormont, Khal Moro, and Drogo's bloodriders. Dany is 13 years old."
